ents</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">? </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Would</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">you</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">like</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">to</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">install</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">additional</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">features</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">with</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">other</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">plugins</span><span class=\"mtk1\">? </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 多選 可以選GA, sitemap, md/mdx</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">Multiple</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">choice</span><span class=\"mtk1\">) </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Use</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">arrow</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">keys</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">to</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">move</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk12\">spacebar</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">to</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">select</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk12\">and</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">confirm</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">with</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">an</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">enter</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">on</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Done&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">❯◯ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">the</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Google</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Analytics</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">tracking</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">script</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◯ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">responsive</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">images</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◉ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">an</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">automatic</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">sitemap</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◯ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Generate</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">manifest</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">file</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◉ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Markdown</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">and</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">MDX</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">support</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◯ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Markdown</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">support</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (</span><span class=\"mtk12\">without</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">MDX</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>我選了 js (後面會提我把 js 轉成 ts 的過程)<br>\n樣式選擇 styled-components<br>\n沒有使用 CMS 而是直接用 md 檔， 所以加裝了 md/mdx support</p>\n<p>完成後 你的網站就可以跑起來了 ～<br>\n在 cmd 中 把本地端伺服器架起來<br>\n<code>npm run develop</code><br>\n然後開啟瀏覽器 輸入網址： <a href=\"http://localhost:8000\">http://localhost:8000</a><br>\n就可以看到你的網站了 🎉<br>\n之後就可以藉由編輯 src/pages/index.js 這個檔案<br>\n然後就可以馬上在畫面上看到更新<br>\n接著我會分享一些功能</p>\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" checked disabled> <a href=\"/blog/form-js-to-ts\">js to ts</a></li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> theme 暗黑模式</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> i18n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> deploy to github-page</li>\n</ul>\n<p>以上是今天的分享 👋</p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n 